T chc bo co nh k

Chng ny bao gm reportfactory package, l mt package h tr vic bo co s dng R Markdown.

Trong cc tnh hung m bn chy bo co thng xuyn (hng ngy, hng tun, v.v.), n gip gim bt vic son nhiu tp R Markdown v t chc cc kt qu u ra ca chng. V bn cht, n cung cp mt nh my m t bn c th chy cc bo co R Markdown, nhn cc th mc c nh du ngy thng v thi gian t ng cho kt qu u ra v c quyn kim sot phin bn nh.

reportfactory l mt trong nhng packages c pht trin bi RECON (R Epidemics Consortium). y l website v Github ca h.

Chun b

Ti packages

T trong RStudio, hy ci t phin bn mi nht ca reportfactory package t Github.

Bn c th thc hin vic ny thng qua pacman package vi p_load_current_gh(), lnh ny s buc nhp phin bn mi nht t Github. Cung cp chui k t reconverse/reportfactory, trong ch nh t chc Github (reconverse) v kho lu tr (reportfactory). Bn cng c th s dng install_github() t remotes package thay th.

# Install and load the latest version of the package from Github
pacman::p_load_current_gh("reconverse/reportfactory")
#remotes::install_github("reconverse/reportfactory") # alternative

Nh my mi

to mt nh my mi, chy hm new_factory(). Thao tc ny s to mt th mc d n R c lp mi. Mc nh l:

  • Nh my s c thm vo th mc lm vic ca bn
  • Tn ca nh my d n R s c gi l new_factory.Rproj
  • Phin RStudio ca bn s chuyn sang d n R ny
# This will create the factory in the working directory
new_factory()

Nhn vo bn trong nh my, bn c th thy rng cc th mc con v mt s tp c to t ng.

  • Th mc report_sources s cha cc scripts R Markdown ca bn, cc scripts ny s to ra cc bo co ca bn
  • Th mc outputs s cha cc kt qu u ra ca bo co (v d: HTML, Word, PDF, v.v.)
  • Th mc scripts c th c s dng lu tr cc scripts R khc (v d: c ly t cc scripts Rmd ca bn)
  • Th mc data c th c s dng cha d liu ca bn (bao gm cc th mc con th v sch)
  • Tp .here, v vy bn c th s dng here package gi cc tp trong th mc con theo mi quan h ca chng vi th mc gc ny (xem chng [R projects] bit thm chi tit)
  • Tp gitignore c to trong trng hp bn lin kt d n R ny vi kho lu tr Github (xem [Version control and collaboration with Github])
  • Tp README trng, nu bn s dng kho lu tr Github

THN TRNG: ty thuc vo ci t my tnh ca bn, cc tp nh .here c th tn ti nhng n.

Trong s cc ci t mc nh, di y l mt s ci t m bn c th iu chnh trong lnh new_factory():

  • factory = - t tn cho th mc gc (mc nh l new_factory)
  • path = - Ch nh ng dn tp cho nh my mi (mc nh l th mc lm vic)
  • report_sources = t tn thay th cho th mc con cha cc R Markdown scripts (mc nh l report_sources)
  • outputs = t tn thay th cho th mc cha kt qu u ra bo co (mc nh l outputs)

Xem ?new_factory bit danh sch y cc i s.

Khi bn to nh my mi, phin R ca bn c chuyn sang d n R mi, v vy bn nn ti li package reportfactory.

pacman::p_load(reportfactory)

By gi bn c th chy lnh factory_overview() xem cu trc bn trong (tt c cc th mc v tp) trong nh my.

factory_overview()            # print overview of the factory to console

Cy cc th mc v tp ca nh sn xut c in ra R console. Lu rng trong th mc data c cc th mc con cho d liu raw (th) v clean (sch) cng nh d liu CSV mu. Ngoi ra cn c example_report.Rmd trong th mc report_sources.

To bo co

T bn trong d n R ca nh my, hy to bo co R Markdown ging nh bn thng lm v lu n vo th mc report_sources. Xem chng [R Markdown][Reports with R Markdown] bit hng dn. v d, chng ti thm nhng th sau vo nh my:

  • R markdown script mi c tn daily_sitrep.Rmd, c lu trong th mc report_sources
  • D liu cho bo co (linelist_cleaned.rds), c lu vo th mc con clean trong th mc data

Chng ta c th thy bng cch s dng factory_overview() R Markdown trong th mc report_sources v tp d liu trong th mc d liu clean (c nh du):

Di y l nh chp phn u ca R Markdown daily_sitrep.Rmd. Bn c th thy rng nh dng u ra c t l HTML, thng qua tiu YAML output: html_document.

Trong script n gin ny, c cc lnh :

  • Ti cc packages cn thit
  • Nhp d liu danh sch dng bng ng dn tp t package here (c thm trong chng [Import and export])
linelist <- import(here("data", "clean", "linelist_cleaned.rds"))
  • In bng tm tt cc trng hp v xut n vi export() di dng tp .csv
  • In mt ng cong dch t v xut n bng ggsave () di dng tp .png

Bn ch c th xem li danh sch cc bo co R Markdown trong th mc report_sources bng lnh ny:

list_reports()

Bin son

Trong nh my bo co, bin son bo co R Markdown c ngha l .Rmd script s c chy v u ra s c to (nh c ch nh trong script YAML, v d nh HTML, Word, PDF, v.v.).

Nh my s t ng to mt th mc c nh du ngy thng v thi gian cho cc kt qu u ra trong th mc outputs.

Bn thn bo co v mi tp xut do script to ra (v d: csv, png, xlsx) s c lu vo th mc ny. Ngoi ra, bn thn script Rmd s c lu trong th mc ny, v vy bn c bn ghi ca phin bn script .

iu ny tri ngc vi hot ng bnh thng ca R Markdown knitted (kt hp), lu kt qu u ra vo v tr ca script Rmd. Hnh vi mc nh ny c th dn n cc th mc ng c, ln xn. Nh my nhm mc ch ci thin t chc khi mt ngi cn chy bo co thng xuyn.

Bin son theo tn

Bn c th bin dch mt bo co c th bng cch chy compile_reports() v t tn Rmd script (khng c phn m rng .Rmd) cho reports =. n gin hn, bn c th b qua reports = v ch cn vit tn R Markdown trong du ngoc kp, nh bn di.

Lnh ny s ch bin dch bo co daily_sitrep.Rmd, lu bo co HTML, xut bng .csv v ng cong dch bnh .png vo mt th mc con c ng du ngy v gi c th cho bo co, trong th mc outputs .

Lu rng nu bn chn cung cp phn m rng .Rmd, bn phi nhp chnh xc phn m rng v n c lu trong tn tp (.rmd so vi .Rmd).

Cng lu rng khi bin son, bn c th thy mt s tp tm thi xut hin trong th mc report_sources - nhng chng s sm bin mt khi chng c chuyn n ng th mc output.

Bin son theo s

Bn cng c th ch nh Rmd script bin dch bng cch cung cp mt s hoc vect s cho reports =. Cc con s phi ph hp vi th t cc bo co xut hin khi bn chy list_reports().

# Compile the second and fourth Rmds in the "report_sources" folder
compile_reports(reports = c(2, 4))

Bin son tt c

Bn c th bin son tt c bo co R Markdown trong th mc report_sources bng cch t i s report = thnh TRUE.

Bin son t th mc con

Bn c th thm cc th mc con vo th mc report_sources. chy bo co R Markdown t mt th mc con, ch cn cung cp tn ca th mc cho subfolder =. Di y l v d v code bin son bo co Rmd nm trong th mc con ca report_sources.

compile_reports(
     reports = "summary_for_partners.Rmd",
     subfolder = "for_partners")

Bn c th bin son tt c cc bo co Rmd trong mt th mc con bng cch cung cp tn th mc con cho reports =, vi mt du gch cho cui, nh bn di.

compile_reports(reports = "for_partners/")

Tham s ha

Nh lu trong chng v [Reports with R Markdown], bn c th chy bo co vi cc thng s c ch nh. Bn c th chuyn cc tham s ny di dng danh sch ti compile_reports () thng qua i s params =. V d, trong bo co h cu ny, c ba tham s c cung cp cho bo co R Markdown.

compile_reports(
  reports = "daily_sitrep.Rmd",
  params = list(most_recent_data = TRUE,
                region = "NORTHERN",
                rates_denominator = 10000),
  subfolder = "regional"
)

Dng run-file

Nu bn c nhiu bo co cn chy, hy cn nhc to R script cha tt c cc lnh compile_reports(). Ngi dng c th ch cn chy tt c cc lnh trong R script ny v tt c cc bo co s c bin son. Bn c th lu run-file ny vo th mc scripts.

Kt qu u ra

Sau khi chng ta bin son cc bo co mt vi ln, th mc outputs c th trng ging nh sau (cc im ni bt c thm vo r rng):

  • Trong outputs, cc th mc con c to cho mi bo co Rmd
  • Trong , cc th mc con khc c to cho mi ln bin son duy nht
    • y l nhng ngy thng v thi gian c ng du (2021-04-23_T11-07-36 c ngha l ngy 23 thng 4 nm 2021 lc 11:07:36)
    • Bn c th chnh sa nh dng du ngy/gi. Xem ?compile_reports
  • Trong mi th mc ngy/gi c bin son, kt qu bo co c lu tr (v d: HTML, PDF, Word) cng vi tp lnh Rmd (kim sot phin bn!) V bt k tp no c xut khc (v d: table.csv, translate_curve.png)

y l ch xem bn trong mt trong cc th mc c nh du ngy/gi cho bo co daily_sitrep. ng dn tp c nh du bng mu vng nhn mnh.

Cui cng, bn di l nh chp mn hnh ca kt qu bo co HTML.

Bn c th s dng list_outputs() xem li danh sch cc kt qu u ra.

Mc khc

Knit

Bn vn c th knit mt trong cc bo co R Markdown ca mnh bng cch nhn nt Knit nu mun. Nu bn lm iu ny, theo mc nh, kt qu u ra s xut hin trong th mc lu Rmd - th mc report_sources. Trong cc phin bn trc ca reportfactory, vic c bt k tp no khng phi Rmd trong report_sources s ngn vic bin dch, nhng trng hp ny khng cn na. Bn c th chy compile_reports() v khng c li no xy ra.

Scripts

Chng ti khuyn khch bn s dng th mc scripts lu tr runfiles hoc cc .R scripts c ly t cc .R scripts ca bn. Xem trang trn [R Markdown][Reports with R Markdown] bit cc mo v cch cu trc code ca bn trn mt s tp.

Thm

  • Vi reportfactory, bn c th s dng hm list_deps() lit k tt c cc packages c yu cu trn tt c cc bo co trong ton b nh my.

  • C mt package i km trong qu trnh pht trin c gi l rfextras cung cp nhiu chc nng tr gip hn h tr bn trong vic xy dng bo co, chng hn nh:

    • load_scripts() - dn ngun/ti tt c cc .R scripts trong mt th mc nht nh (th mc scripts theo mc nh)
    • find_latest() - tm phin bn mi nht ca tp (v d: tp d liu mi nht)
